Source: opendnp3
Section: libs
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Chris Verges <chris.verges@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), dh-autoreconf, autoconf, automake, libtool, oracle-java7-installer | oracle-java8-installer, oracle-java7-set-default | oracle-java8-set-default
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Homepage: http://dnp3.github.io

Package: libopendnp3
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: A C++ library for the OpenDNP3 stack
 This package provides C++ bindings for the OpenDNP3 stack.  This stack
 implements both a DNP3 master and DNP3 outstation.

Package: libopendnp3-java
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libopendnp3
Description: Java Native Interface (JNI) library for the OpenDNP3 stack
 This package provides a JNI library for the C++-based OpenDNP3 stack.

Package: libopendnp3-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libopendnp3, libopendnp3-java
Recommends: libopendnp3-cpp-demos, libopendnp3-java-demos
Description: C++/Java development files for the OpenDNP3 stack
 This package provides complimentary C++ and Java files for development
 with the Automatak DNP3 stack.

Package: libopendnp3-cpp-demos
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: C++ master/outstation demos for the OpenDNP3 stack
 This package provides C++ master/outstation demos.

Package: libopendnp3-java-demos
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libopendnp3-java
Description: Java master/outstation demos for the OpenDNP3 stack
 This package provides Java master/outstation demos.
